data.name: gunaLabel73.Text
data.value: There is a review system where a Buyer will give a review to the Seller for his work and can give bonus if he wants to do so. A Seller can also give a review to the Buyer. Here it is notable that admin will not get any commission from the bonus.

data.name: gunaLabel96.Text
data.value: Admin of the system will get 10% for every job if the Buyer accept the job which is submitted by the Seller. Suppose if the job in worth of 70$ then a Seller will get 63$(without bonus) and admin will get 7$ for the maintenance of the System.

data.name: gunaLabel89.Text
data.value: A seller can see the description of the job and can request to get that. If Buyer accepts his request, then the status of that job will be Pending and after finishing the job Seller has to submit that to the Buyer through a submission link.
